title: Start
body:
Jane: John you made me do this now Timmy will pay the price
"John is trying to speak but nothing is coming out"
Jane: Dont worry my love we will be together soon.
"Jane heads downstairs to find Timmy"
Jane: Timmy your fathers been hurt, we need to go upstairs
Timmy: nooo quickly lets go help him
"they both head upstairs"
"Timmy runs over to John on the ground who is barely alive"
Timmy: Father please be okay i cant lose u too
"John again is trying to speak to warn Timmy, but nothing is coming out"
Jane" Pulls out her gun and shoots Timmy in the head"
Jane: John we are going to stay a family forever, no one is leaving
"Jane lays down with john then shoots herself"
The end
